Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:01:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了  突然把大家叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  跟我來就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們上次碰面是在游泳池的時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很擔心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏姐  你把我們叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是為了讓我們和小櫻見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  櫻說想見你們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻  出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天就要離開這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說離開…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天玩一整天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  有什麼不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最後  就讓我們給她創造一份快樂的回憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不喜歡太傷感的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是就算說要玩  要去哪裡玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去游泳池嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻  你有想去的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個畫上去  這樣就大功告成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不覺得太誇張了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛可沒有這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請重拍一張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  我們一起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小櫻好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  夏露露姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想和小隆拍雙人照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你就忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能做的也就只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日式點心？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菜單裡有這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說小櫻喜歡日式點心  就特地請店裡做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  歌丸的份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我平時不怎麼吃日式點心  但這還挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會吃上癮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  小櫻竟然喜歡日式點心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來相當喜歡古樸的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要變冷清了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻不在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易成為了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是你的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻和我們永遠都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事嗎  櫻突然說要離開這個小島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏  你知道些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻要離開這裡的事  我也是昨天知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是櫻做的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想為她作見證
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  早知道要來海邊  我就帶上泳衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要下海的話季節還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊  會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好涼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得來到海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在這裡  初音島就能一覽無遺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣望過去  真是個很小的島啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清隆同學的社區在那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這麼多房子可不好找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊以前是個廣場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  你想起什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬乃以前在那個廣場摔倒過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候哄你不哭可費了我很大勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有過那樣的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了  沉醉在兩個人的回憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是個很小的島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以每個地方都充滿了回憶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我們是時候該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再借給你一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  大家走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下  立夏姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就要和哥哥分別了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約會  約會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和哥哥約會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著害羞啊  因為這是約會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  這是哪門子的約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡從這裡看海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  和小櫻第一次相遇也是在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直看著大海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我跟你搭話  你也一副悵然若失的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在仍然記憶猶新啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你突然之間說要離開…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊  櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  笑一笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的約會  你這樣一點都不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能跟哥哥笑著道別
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來去哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是休息日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得  在這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道在那種地方居然有個能進入學校的小洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我很瞭解這所學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.40,0:14:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快要開畢業派對了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始做準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得有點寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  畢業也是啟程的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥將來想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎？現在還沒有決定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻將來想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠認識到這麼多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後還能和哥哥約會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是應該跟哥哥說清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永不凋零的櫻花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能實現任何願望的魔法櫻花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我做個約定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相隔20年櫻花再次盛開的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再一次出現在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該存在的地方並不是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上要去和重要的人見面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道能不能相見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能相見的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻的思念肯定能傳達過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很像我重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:18:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個怎樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個平時總是很懶散的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  他是個溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論何時都可以回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永遠是櫻的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能和哥哥相遇真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的傍晚  來看看永不凋零的櫻花樹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個的約定和小小的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論經過幾十年  幾百年都不會改變的  重要的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終回  Da Capo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越時空的奇跡  此刻又開始了輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:37.24,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君の声  その笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:41.24,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}弾むように  届くから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:49.29,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}続く空の先へと  思いは駆けてく
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:53.30,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}桜舞う  時の風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:57.37,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}その香り  煌きと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:02.26,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}寄せては返す思い
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.23,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ここに満ちて揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:09.29,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君が好きなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:13.72,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}言ってしまいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:21.26,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}お喋りの欠片たち  願いを包めば
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:29.49,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不意に切なくて  心を隠してた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:39.01,INlrcJPN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}降り注ぐ光の行方    どこへ行くの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:37.24,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的音容笑貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:41.24,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令我不禁心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:49.29,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}把心中的思念放飛  向著藍天的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:53.30,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}櫻花飄舞  時光如風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:57.37,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}花香甜美  花瓣閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:02.26,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}回憶如浪花般翻飛起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.23,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}搖蕩著填滿了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:09.29,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我好喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:13.72,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:21.26,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在片言隻語中  包含著最真摯的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:29.49,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悲傷不經意地略過心頭  令我不禁藏起對你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:39.01,INlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天空中灑下的光芒  究竟會照向何方
